::Firearm::

Firearm reaches the CR chambers, looking back at Deemos and Inzola. "Here you 
are. Hurry up and get in, there's a battle outside that requires my 
attention!"

The ship's shields, shock absorbers, and sound absorbers were blocking out 
all sounds of battle, but he knew that it was still going on. He would wait 
till Deemos and Inzola entered the chamber, then he'd lock the door, go 
outside, and slag 'imself some Preds!
